      <h1>Our Pre-Nursery</h1>
      <p>Explore our Pre-Nursery, where active toddlers continue their early learning journey in a playful, structured, and supportive setting.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Development-Focused Environment:</strong> Our Pre-Nursery rooms are bright, safe, and created for early exploration and hands-on learning.</li>
        <li><strong>Qualified Early Years Teachers:</strong> Our staff use age-appropriate methods to encourage curiosity, language, and social confidence.</li>
        <li><strong>Playful Learning:</strong> We blend play with guided activities to strengthen motor skills, problem solving, and communication.</li>
        <li><strong>Whole-Child Growth:</strong> Lessons support physical activity, emotional wellbeing, creativity, and Christian character formation.</li>
      </ul>
      <img src="/images/people/our-admission.webp" alt="Pre-Nursery Classroom" style="max-width: 100%; margin-top: 1em; border-radius: 8px;" loading="lazy">
